{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"935c3e5c41","title":"胡乔木致北京邮电学院全体革命同志的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7fbf0f0fa2","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":12,"articleId":"935c3e5c41","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"胡乔木","id":"3fd96bb002","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"0db92e520a","name":"胡乔木"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"89d9051198","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3656d11c9b","type":"title","text":"胡乔木致北京邮电学院全体革命同志的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ff332b831a","type":"subtitle","text":"（胡乔木的一张大字报）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a4f647621","type":"paragraph","text":"北京邮电学院全体革命同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e61307071f","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十八日我在邮电学院曾说：以朱春和为首的工作组是革命的，这是完全错误的。是为资产阶级反动路线效劳。派工作组到学校，就是资产阶级反动路线。就是与以毛主席为代表的无产阶级革命路线相对抗的，施行资产阶级反动路线，就必然要镇压革命群众运动，破坏无产阶级文化大革命。邮电学院发生的情况完全证实了这点。我在8月24日的答复邮电学院侯泽民、郑义增等十六同学的来信时，已经承认我那次关于工作组的话是错误的，并请他们转告全体同学。现在特再次诚恳地向你们承认错误，并对于你们彻底批判资产阶级反动路线的革命斗争，表示最热烈最坚决地拥护和支持。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3b2ae7bfe7","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命万岁！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4e9bbccb1","type":"paragraph","text":"以毛主席为代表的无产阶级革命路线万岁！","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67586e2684","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的伟大导师、伟大领袖、伟大统帅、伟大舵手毛主席万岁！万岁！万万岁！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53484bf16e","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"07dc8a0ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"革命敬礼","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7599ee66e7","type":"paragraph","text":"胡乔木   十月十二日","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"935c3e5c41","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}